"1 tablespoon canola oil","1 pound skinless, boneless chicken breast, cut into bite-sized pieces","3/4 teaspoon salt, divided","1/2 cup vertically sliced onion","2 teaspoons minced fresh garlic","2 teaspoons ground cumin","1 teaspoon ground coriander","1/2 teaspoon dried oregano","1/4 teaspoon ground red pepper","3 cups no-salt-added canned cannellini beans, rinsed and drained","1 cup water","2  (4-ounce) cans chopped green chiles, undrained and divided","1  (14-ounce) can fat-free, lower-sodium chicken broth","1/4 cup cilantro leaves","1  lime, cut into 8 wedges"